text: I’m a bit biased—any place that serves Guinness Draught automatically gets a minimum of 4 stars from me. The calamari here is exceptional: perfectly crispy on the outside and tender inside. Plus, the staff are genuinely friendly. This is officially my go-to weekend bar. 5 ⭐️.
Coz I got the best seat indoors. For outdoor is ok. Great that now have big screen to watch live sports like soccer etc.. the staff is super friendly. I've came here plenty of times..

Love their chicken quesadillas . Nice environment to chill with friends / colleagues after work . 👍🏻

But needa improve on the fish & chips . Fish abit too soft & the outer crispy skin is too thick ..  but overall food stil acceptable…

A good place with a variety of drinks and a decent selection of food. Service was good and quick. Everyone seemed to know each other and a good atmosphere all around. Food was decent and you can't go wrong with the beer.

The best place in town!
Beer is great and at low price all day long, the Rendang is beyond amazing especially considering it’s a bar and the people who hang out as well as the staff can’t make you feel more at home! My living room! 🙏🏾😎
